<ab facs="#facs_325_r1l16">Alſo <expan>laſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wiſſen / daʒ vvir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_325_r1l17">etlıche <expan>fürſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vmb vns geſeʒʒen / cʒü einander 
